            "stanza_text": "Au Luxembourg, que je dis\nBeau comme le paradis,\nOn a torturé les lignes\nEt le fantasque dessin\nD'un capricieux bassin,\nPour les canards et les cygnes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Les bleus canards du Japon",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Semblent sortis d'un crépon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et forment un long cortège",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "A l'entour des cygnes blancs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Dont les ailes et les flancs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Sont pareils à de la neige.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les bleus canards du Japon\nSemblent sortis d'un crépon,\nEt forment un long cortège\nA l'entour des cygnes blancs,\nDont les ailes et les flancs\nSont pareils à de la neige."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Tout au beau milieu des eaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Une île offre à ces oiseaux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Le gazon vert. Leur royaume",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Est fort exigu. Mais on",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Leur a fait une maison",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Basse, avec un toit de chaume.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout au beau milieu des eaux,\nUne île offre à ces oiseaux\nLe gazon vert. Leur royaume\nEst fort exigu. Mais on\nLeur a fait une maison\nBasse, avec un toit de chaume."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "En leurs infinis loisirs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ils savourent les plaisirs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Que l'oisiveté ménage ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et philosophes par goût,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Les uns ne font rien du tout,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Pendant que le reste nage.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "En leurs infinis loisirs,\nIls savourent les plaisirs\nQue l'oisiveté ménage ;\nEt philosophes par goût,\nLes uns ne font rien du tout,\nPendant que le reste nage."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Mais dans l'île, sur le bord",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Que l'eau caressante mord",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Et parmi les folles branches,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Parfois, d'un mouvement fou,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Les cygnes lèvent leur cou",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Puis ouvrent leurs ailes blanches.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais dans l'île, sur le bord\nQue l'eau caressante mord\nEt parmi les folles branches,\nParfois, d'un mouvement fou,\nLes cygnes lèvent leur cou\nPuis ouvrent leurs ailes blanches."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Les grands cygnes fabuleux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Et les petits canards bleus",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Respirent dans la nature",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Et, leur sens étant profond,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Ces êtres ailés ne font",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Jamais de littérature.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les grands cygnes fabuleux\nEt les petits canards bleus\nRespirent dans la nature\nEt, leur sens étant profond,\nCes êtres ailés ne font\nJamais de littérature."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "C'est la joie, argent comptant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Certes, je serais content",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Si de tels bonheurs insignes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "M'étaient seulement promis,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "O vous, canards, mes amis,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Et vous, mes confrères, cygnes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est la joie, argent comptant.\nCertes, je serais content\nSi de tels bonheurs insignes\nM'étaient seulement promis,\nO vous, canards, mes amis,\nEt vous, mes confrères, cygnes !"
        }
